- THANK GOODNESS.

47
00:04:19,083 --> 00:04:20,291
- UH--

48
00:04:20,375 --> 00:04:22,208
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH FOR SAYING
SO, KAORU-SAMA.

49
00:04:22,291 --> 00:04:24,000
- OH, HEY,
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BOW.

50
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:25,375
COME ON.

51
00:04:27,458 --> 00:04:30,791
- ACTUALLY, THIS KIMONO WAS
GIVEN TO ME BY MY GRANDMOTHER.

52
00:04:30,875 --> 00:04:32,458
- OHH, IS THAT TRUE?

53
00:04:32,541 --> 00:04:34,416
WERE YOU CLOSE TO
YOUR GRANDMOTHER, AOI-CHAN?

54
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:37,458
- YES. BOTH MY FATHER AND MOTHER
WERE ALWAYS BUSY WITH WORK

55
00:04:37,541 --> 00:04:38,875
WHILE I WAS GROWING UP.

56
00:04:38,958 --> 00:04:41,333
SO SHE TOOK CARE
OF ME OFTEN.

57
00:04:41,416 --> 00:04:42,916
SHE WAS SUCH A KIND PERSON.

58
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,083
I LOVED HER VERY MUCH.

59
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:47,583
SHE PASSED AWAY
FIVE YEARS AGO, UNFORTUNATELY.

60
00:04:47,666 --> 00:04:49,750
- I'M SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

61
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,458
HUH?

62
00:04:52,541 --> 00:04:54,375
WHY DID YOU STOP WALKING,
AOI-CHAN?

63
00:05:03,166 --> 00:05:05,250
- CHERRY BLOSSOMS.

64
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:06,458
- Kaoru: AOI-CHAN?

65
00:05:06,541 --> 00:05:09,125
- UH-- OHH.

66
00:05:10,541 --> 00:05:12,416
WHEN I WAS YOUNG,
MY GRANDMOTHER WOULD TAKE ME

67
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,125
TO SEE THE CHERRY BLOSSOMS.

68
00:05:14,208 --> 00:05:15,541
EACH AND EVERY YEAR.

69
00:05:17,125 --> 00:05:18,291
AND WHEN SHE DID,

70
00:05:18,375 --> 00:05:20,500
GRANDMOTHER WOULD ALWAYS
BE WEARING THIS KIMONO. 

71
00:05:20,583 --> 00:05:22,583
I LOVED THIS KIMONO,

72
00:05:22,666 --> 00:05:24,333
AND I OFTEN
FUSSED OVER IT,

73
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:26,916
SAYING THAT I WANTED ONE
JUST LIKE IT.

74
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,750
- GRANDMA, AOI WANTS A KIMONO
JUST LIKE YOURS.

75
00:05:29,833 --> 00:05:31,208
I WANT ONE, I WANT ONE!

76
00:05:31,291 --> 00:05:32,583
- GOODNESS GRACIOUS.

77
00:05:32,666 --> 00:05:35,250
YOU WANT A KIMONO OVER
WESTERN STYLE CLOTHES?

78
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:37,041
YOU'RE A KIMONO
MERCHANT ALREADY.

79
00:05:37,125 --> 00:05:38,875
- YEAH.
DON'T YOU KNOW, GRANDMA?

80
00:05:38,958 --> 00:05:40,125
I LOVE KIMONOS!

81
00:05:40,208 --> 00:05:42,166
- IS THAT SO?

82
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,708
THEN PLEASE, AOI,

83
00:05:43,791 --> 00:05:45,291
NEVER FORGET THIS ONE THING.

84
00:05:45,375 --> 00:05:47,458
ALL KIMONOS
ARE VERY SPECIAL,

85
00:05:47,541 --> 00:05:50,208
BECAUSE THEY ARE OVERFLOWING
WITH THE FEELINGS AND EMOTIONS

86
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:52,750
OF THOSE WHO WEAR THEM.

87
00:05:52,833 --> 00:05:56,000
SO WHEN YOU WEAR A KIMONO THAT
ORIGINAL BELONGED TO ANOTHER,

88
00:05:56,083 --> 00:05:58,125
YOU ARE ALSO WEARING
THE FEELINGS OF THAT PERSON

89
00:05:58,208 --> 00:05:59,666
THAT THE KIMONO HAS FELT.

90
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,666
- WHAT THE KIMONO HAS FELT?

91
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:03,250
- YOU'RE STILL YOUNG,

92
00:06:03,333 --> 00:06:05,125
SO THIS MAY BE
A LITTLE HARD TO UNDERSTAND.

93
00:06:06,250 --> 00:06:07,166
AOI...

94
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:09,583
WHEN YOU BECOME OLDER,

95
00:06:09,666 --> 00:06:10,791
THIS KIMONO IS YOURS.

96
00:06:10,875 --> 00:06:11,916
- REALLY, GRANDMA?

97
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,916
- SO PLEASE,
WEAR IT WHEN YOU HAVE

98
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,125
A LEISURELY STROLL
LIKE THIS,

99
00:06:16,208 --> 00:06:18,250
WALKING TOGETHER WITH
THE PERSON YOU'LL MARRY.

100
00:06:18,333 --> 00:06:21,250
- OH, I ALREADY KNOW
WHO THAT PERSON WILL BE.

101
00:06:21,333 --> 00:06:23,125
- OH?
- AOI WILL BE TOGETHER

102
00:06:23,208 --> 00:06:25,625
WITH KAORU-SAMA
OF THE HANABISHIS.

103
00:06:25,708 --> 00:06:28,250
- I SEE.
ONE OF THE HANABISHIS.

104
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:30,583
THAT MAKES PERFECT SENSE.

105
00:06:30,666 --> 00:06:33,083
IN MY YOUNGER DAYS,
I TOOK MANY A WALK 

106
00:06:33,166 --> 00:06:35,250
WITH YOUR GRANDFATHER
WEARING THIS KIMONO. 

107
00:06:35,333 --> 00:06:36,750
YOU KNOW, AOI,

108
00:06:36,833 --> 00:06:39,708
YOUR GRANDFATHER LOVED THIS
KIMONO MORE THAN ANY OTHER.

109
00:06:39,791 --> 00:06:41,750
IF THE FEELINGS
HELD IN THIS KIMONO

110
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:43,583
ARE ONE DAY PASSED
DOWN UNTO YOU,

111
00:06:43,666 --> 00:06:45,916
THEN THAT BOY OF
THE HANABISHIS WILL SURELY--

112
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:49,875
HE WILL SURELY
LIKE THIS KIMONO AS WELL.

113
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:54,916
- WHEN I WAS YOUNGER,

114
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,083
I DIDN'T REALLY UNDERSTAND
WHAT MY GRANDMOTHER

115
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:58,291
WAS TALKING ABOUT.

116
00:06:59,625 --> 00:07:01,500
BUT I UNDERSTAND IT
QUITE WELL NOW.

117
00:07:04,166 --> 00:07:06,125
THIS KIMONO OVERFLOWS

118
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:09,625
WITH THE LOVE YOU FEEL FOR THE
PERSON WHO'S DEAREST TO YOU.

119
00:07:12,666 --> 00:07:14,250
- WOW.

120
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:15,791
THAT'S AN INCREDIBLE STORY.

121
00:07:18,958 --> 00:07:21,083
- KAORU-SAMA.
- HUH?

122
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:23,416
- STANDING HERE WITH YOU
WEARING THIS KIMONO

123
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:25,625
MAKES ME FEEL LIKE I'M
FALLING MORE AND MORE

124
00:07:25,708 --> 00:07:27,208
IN LOVE WITH YOU EVERY MOMENT.

125
00:07:27,291 --> 00:07:28,583
- ( stammers )

126
00:07:30,166 --> 00:07:31,625
- ( sighs )

127
00:07:31,708 --> 00:07:34,416
SO THAT'S WHY I'VE ALWAYS 
WANTED TO WEAR THIS KIMONO

128
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,583
AND STEP OUTSIDE
FOR A STROLL WITH YOU.

129
00:07:36,666 --> 00:07:37,583
THANK YOU.

130
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:39,250
- OH. SO THAT'S
WHAT IS WAS, HUH?

131
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:41,250
