EMBARRASSED BY IT ALL.

132
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,500
LET'S SEE, THIS LOOKS LIKE
EVERYTHING WE HAD TO BUY,

133
00:07:48,583 --> 00:07:49,375
I THINK.

134
00:07:49,458 --> 00:07:51,125
- ( chuckles )
- AOI-CHAN?

135
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:54,916
- LOOK AT THIS,
KAORU-SAMA.

136
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,708
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED OVER HERE?

137
00:07:56,791 --> 00:07:58,583
- THIS PLACE IS...

138
00:07:58,666 --> 00:08:00,750
( gasps )
OH YEAH.

139
00:08:00,833 --> 00:08:03,583
THIS IS WHERE YOU AND I
MET AGAIN AFTER ALL THOSE YEARS.

140
00:08:03,666 --> 00:08:04,583
- THAT'S RIGHT.

141
00:08:04,666 --> 00:08:06,583
IT WAS QUITE A COINCIDENCE

142
00:08:06,666 --> 00:08:08,583
THAT YOU HAPPENED TO
PASS BY THAT DAY

143
00:08:08,666 --> 00:08:10,583
TO FIX THE STRAP
ON MY SANDAL.

144
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:12,541
I REALLY APPRECIATED IT.

145
00:08:12,625 --> 00:08:14,916
- Kaoru: I'M USUALLY
NOT THAT NICE TO OTHER PEOPLE,

146
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,541
BUT FOR SOME REASON
THAT DAY

147
00:08:16,625 --> 00:08:18,500
I WAS REALLY WORRIED ABOUT YOU,
AOI-CHAN.

148
00:08:20,333 --> 00:08:22,916
- Both: HMM?
- WHAT?

149
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,708
HEY, WHY WON'T THIS
GATE LET ME PASS?

150
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:26,583
THAT'S STRANGE.

151
00:08:26,666 --> 00:08:28,166
- ( both chuckle )
- WELL, WHAT SHOULD I DO?

152
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:29,833
- EXCUSE ME.

