00:08:29,916 --> 00:08:31,208
WHAT SEEMS TO BE
THE MATTER?

154
00:08:31,291 --> 00:08:32,166
- OH, WELL...

155
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,250
THANK YOU FOR THE HELP
YOU'VE GIVEN ME.  SEE YOU.

156
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,250
- ( chuckles )

157
00:08:39,333 --> 00:08:41,583
I ALMOST FEEL AS IF
MY PAST SELF

158
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:43,208
IS REFLECTED
IN THE PRESENT.

159
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:44,875
- THAT REMINDS ME,
YOU REMEMBER HOW YOU AND I

160
00:08:44,958 --> 00:08:47,250
TOOK THE TRAIN TOGETHER
TO IZUMIGAOKA.

161
00:08:47,333 --> 00:08:48,458
- I DO.

162
00:08:48,541 --> 00:08:49,791
BUT NOW THAT
I THINK ABOUT IT,

163
00:08:49,875 --> 00:08:51,250
