WE ARRIVED THERE

164
00:08:51,333 --> 00:08:52,750
ONLY A FEW MOMENTS
AFTER WE BOARDED. 

165
00:08:52,833 --> 00:08:55,166
- ( chuckles ) ACTUALLY,
WHAT HAPPENED BACK THEN 

166
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:56,833
WAS THAT YOU FELL ASLEEP

167
00:08:56,916 --> 00:08:58,625
AND WE ENDED UP
GOING ALL THE WAY AROUND

168
00:08:58,708 --> 00:09:00,125
BEFORE GETTING OFF
AT THE STATION.

169
00:09:00,208 --> 00:09:02,416
- Aoi: WHAT?
IS THAT REALLY TRUE?

170
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,083
I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT THAT.

171
00:09:04,166 --> 00:09:06,208
I WAS WORN OUT AFTER
ALL THE EXCITEMENT. 

172
00:09:06,291 --> 00:09:08,916
( gasps )
WAS THAT ALL I DID, KAORU-SAMA?

173
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,333
