THAT I TROUBLED YOU?

174
00:09:11,416 --> 00:09:12,958
- I'M NOT SURE
WHAT YOU MEAN.

175
00:09:13,041 --> 00:09:15,125
- WELL, FOR INSTANCE,
SLEEP WALKING?

176
00:09:15,208 --> 00:09:17,583
- NOTHING LIKE THAT WENT ON.
YOU SLEPT SOUNDLY.

177
00:09:17,666 --> 00:09:20,083
OH, BUT I GUESS THERE WAS
A LITTLE DROOLING GOING ON.

178
00:09:20,166 --> 00:09:21,583
- WHAT?

179
00:09:21,666 --> 00:09:24,083
- NOT REALLY.
I'M ONLY KIDDING.

180
00:09:24,166 --> 00:09:25,583
- ( sighs )

181
00:09:25,666 --> 00:09:28,500
- HOW COULD YOU BE
SO HORRIBLE, KAORU-SAMA?

182
00:09:33,125 --> 00:09:36,333
- Kaoru: I REMEMBER WHEN
I FIRST CAME TO TOKYO.

183
00:09:38,333 --> 00:09:41,250
- KAORU-SAMA?
KAORU-SAMA?

184
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:43,291
IS ANYTHING THE MATTER,
KAORU-SAMA?

185
00:09:45,125 --> 00:09:47,250
- SAY, AOI-CHAN,
WANT TO TAG ALONG?

186
00:09:47,333 --> 00:09:49,291
- TAG ALONG?
WHERE WILL WE BE GOING?

187
00:09:49,375 --> 00:09:51,250
- THE APARTMENT.

188
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:54,000
THE APARTMENT WHERE
I USED TO LIVE.

189
00:09:54,083 --> 00:09:55,833
- KAORU-SAMA.

190
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:02,750
- THIS PLACE HASN'T
EVEN CHANGED A BIT.

191
00:10:02,833 --> 00:10:05,541
SO, DO YOU WANT TO
GO UP TO THE ROOM?

192
00:10:05,625 --> 00:10:06,500
- SURE.

193
00:10:08,083 --> 00:10:10,291
- I GUESS THEY HAVEN'T
FOUND A RENTER FOR THIS PLACE.

194
00:10:13,416 --> 00:10:14,291
( gasps )

195
00:10:17,666 --> 00:10:19,458
LOOKS LIKE IT'S OPEN.

196
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,500
SURE BRINGS BACK MEMORIES.

197
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:38,458
- THIS PLACE HOLDS SOME 
MEMORIES FOR ME AS WELL.

198
00:10:38,541 --> 00:10:41,000
THERE WERE SO MANY
UNFORGETTABLE MOMENTS

199
00:10:41,083 --> 00:10:43,000
IN THIS ONE SMALL ROOM
AFTER ALL.

200
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:44,416
- THERE SURE WERE.

201
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,583
- OCCASIONALLY,
I HAVE THIS RECURRING DREAM.

202
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:25,583
- RECURRING?
- YES.

203
00:11:25,666 --> 00:11:28,083
IT'S A DREAM ABOUT
BEING WITH YOU IN THIS ROOM

204
00:11:28,166 --> 00:11:29,416
WE'RE STANDING IN,

205
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:31,541
BUT THE KAORU-SAMA
THAT I ALWAYS SEE 

206
00:11:31,625 --> 00:11:33,125
IN THIS RECURRING DREAM

207
00:11:33,208 --> 00:11:34,583
NEVER SAYS ANYTHING.

208
00:11:34,666 --> 00:11:38,500
NOT A SINGLE WORD,
NO MATTER WHAT TOPIC I BRING UP.

209
00:11:38,583 --> 00:11:42,458
I PREPARED MANY MEALS
FOR THAT SILENT KAORU-SAMA.

210
00:11:43,833 --> 00:11:46,458
PLEASE, GO AHEAD AND
START EATING, KAORU-SAMA.

211
00:11:46,541 --> 00:11:49,583
HOWEVER, NO MATTER
WHAT I DID,

212
00:11:49,666 --> 00:11:52,583
WHETHER IT WAS WATCHING
TELEVISION WITH THAT KAORU-SAMA,

213
00:11:52,666 --> 00:11:54,083
READING BOOKS WITH HIM,

214
00:11:54,166 --> 00:11:56,250
ENGAGING IN
LIVELY CONVERSATION,

215
00:11:56,333 --> 00:11:59,250
HE WOULDN'T DO ANYTHING.

216
00:11:59,333 --> 00:12:02,708
DESPITE EVERYTHING,
HE WOULD JUST REMAIN SILENT.

217
00:12:02,791 --> 00:12:06,250
I HAD NO IDEA
WHAT TO DO.

218
00:12:06,333 --> 00:12:08,000
WHEN I THOUGHT OF
THE POSSIBILITY

219
00:12:08,083 --> 00:12:09,916
THAT HE MIGHT
NO LONGER LIKE ME,

220
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,583
IT FELT SO PAINFUL.

221
00:12:12,666 --> 00:12:15,125
ONE TEAR WOULD FALL
AFTER ANOTHER.

222
00:12:15,208 --> 00:12:17,916
THAT IS THE MOMENT
I ALWAYS WAKE UP, 

223
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,916
AND THE MOMENT THAT
I ALWAYS REALIZE

224
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,916
THAT WHAT HAD
REALLY OCCURRED

225
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:26,458
WAS THAT I HAD
FALLEN ASLEEP CRYING.

226
00:12:26,541 --> 00:12:27,916
IT'S JUST A DREAM,

227
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,916
ONLY A DREAM
AND NOTHING MORE.

228
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,916
BUT UNCERTAINTIES ALWAYS
FILL MY MIND REGARDLESS.

229
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,250
I WONDER WHY THAT IS.

230
00:12:35,333 --> 00:12:37,166
- AOI-CHAN.

231
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,291
( gasps )

232
00:12:42,041 --> 00:12:43,125
( sighs )

233
00:12:43,208 --> 00:12:45,583
- I APOLOGIZE,
KAORU-SAMA.

